  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "In the face of advancements, it is necessary to leverage digital technology, not just as a tool for efficiency but also as a dynamic medium for educational transformation, making learning a collaborative, exploratory and empowering process.",
    "Particularly in mathematics education, technology has become a pivotal tool for engaging students and transforming the teaching and learning process.",
    "The evolution of technology has led to the emergence of powerful applications, such as GeoGebra, Google SketchUp and Sketchpad, which have revolutionized the way mathematical concepts are taught and understood, making them more tangible and accessible for learners.",
    "This strategic integration of technology in mathematics education has been widely embraced as it fosters a symbiotic relationship between students, teachers and the available resources, resulting in a more effective learning environment (National Council of Teachers of Mathematics [NCTM], 2015 [NCTM],, 2018)).",
    "The integration of technological advancements within the realm of mathematics education has emerged as a substantial focal point in academic research."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "This strategic integration of technology in mathematics education has been widely embraced as it fosters a symbiotic relationship between students, teachers and the available resources, resulting in a more effective learning environment (National Council of Teachers of Mathematics [NCTM], 2015 [NCTM],, 2018))."
